<item>
            <title>[VALIDATOR-305] Some TLDs are missing from DomainValidator</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/VALIDATOR-305</link>
                <project id="12310494" key="VALIDATOR">Commons Validator</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As reported on list &amp;lt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mail-archive.com/dev@commons.apache.org/msg29436.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.mail-archive.com/dev@commons.apache.org/msg29436.html&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt;, DomainValidator is missing some of the new TLDs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The full list is available from &amp;lt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://data.iana.org/TLD/tlds-alpha-by-domain.txt&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://data.iana.org/TLD/tlds-alpha-by-domain.txt&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12545172">VALIDATOR-305</key>
            <summary>Some TLDs are missing from DomainValidator</summary>
